adventure2D.project

Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • adventure2D.project.GObject
      • adventure2D.project.GameObject

  • public class GameObject
extends GObject
    A class representing a object in the game's world. Objects has x,y coordinates, radius and (only) speed to one direction (both x and y). IMPORTANT NOTE: GObject is actually what the term game object means, this class represent objects like "bullet's" not characters alike. (A good name would have been object...but already in use)
